            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg">Proactive vs. reactive</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ip-white-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            PM tools tell you a task is overdue after it's overdue. The Living Plan detects drift as it happens &mdash; when delivery is diverging from the plan, before it becomes a missed deadline.
