            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-white/30 mb-1">Traditional PM tools</p>
              <p class="text-ip-white-muted">Red status appears after the fact. You find out when it's already late.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-orange-400/5 border border-orange-400/10 rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-orange-400/60 mb-1">Living Plan</p>
              <p class="text-ip-white-muted">Drift flagged as signals diverge. Problems surface while there's still time to act.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Execution vs. administration -->
        <div class="bg-ip-navy-surface border border-ip-border rounded-xl p-6 card-elevated">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-ip-periwinkle/10 border border-ip-periwinkle/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-5 h-5 text-ip-periwinkle"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg">Execution vs. administration</h3>
