              <p class="text-ip-white-muted">6–8 hours per person per week spent keeping plans current. That's the overhead.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-ip-periwinkle/5 border border-ip-periwinkle/10 rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-ip-periwinkle/60 mb-1">Living Plan</p>
              <p class="text-ip-white-muted">Zero hours. The plan maintains itself. That time goes back to actual work.</p>
