        <p class="text-ip-navy/60 text-lg max-w-[52ch] mx-auto">
          AI notetakers capture what happened. But a transcript in a shared doc doesn&rsquo;t change anything &mdash; the plan is still out of date, the missed commitment is still missed. The Living Plan acts on the capture.
